message.body: Hey, it's ####! Are you free tomorrow night? I got VIP tix to the Blues Fest.
Woah! That's sounds awesome.. I'm sad to say I have plans for tomorrow night. Let's do something soon though maybe next week?
Yeah, they just fell into my lap! Next week sounds good...we're free most nights and ######'s out of town Thurs-Mon if you want to do a girly thing.
